{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":240,"text":"As the highest military commander\nof the Netherlands,"},{"time":5400,"text":"with troops stationed around the world,"},{"time":8440,"text":"I'm really honored to be here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12600,"text":"When I look around\nthis TEDxAmsterdam venue,"},{"time":16800,"text":"I see a very special audience."},{"time":20960,"text":"You are the reason why I said yes"},{"time":24888,"text":"to the invitation to come here today."},{"time":29520,"text":"When I look around, I see people\nwho want to make a contribution."},{"time":35320,"text":"I see people who want\nto make a better world,"},{"time":40040,"text":"by doing groundbreaking scientific work,"},{"time":44000,"text":"by creating impressive works of art,"},{"time":47600,"text":"by writing critical articles\nor inspiring books,"},{"time":52840,"text":"by starting up sustainable businesses."},{"time":56360,"text":"And you all have chosen\nyour own instruments"},{"time":60760,"text":"to fulfill this mission\nof creating a better world."},{"time":65480,"text":"Some chose the microscope\nas their instrument."},{"time":69600,"text":"Others chose dancing or painting,"},{"time":72911,"text":"or making music like we just heard."},{"time":75840,"text":"Some chose the pen."},{"time":78560,"text":"Others work through\nthe instrument of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83040,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,\nI made a different choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100840,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105680,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111120,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117031,"text":"I share your goals."},{"time":120240,"text":"I share the goals\nof the speakers you heard before."},{"time":125520,"text":"I did not choose to take up the pen,"},{"time":131560,"text":"the brush,"},{"time":133600,"text":"the camera."},{"time":135560,"text":"I chose this instrument."},{"time":139440,"text":"I chose the gun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143040,"text":"For you, and you heard already,"},{"time":145520,"text":"being so close to this gun\nmay make you feel uneasy."},{"time":152480,"text":"It may even feel scary."},{"time":155040,"text":"A real gun at a few feet's distance."},{"time":159480,"text":"Let us stop for a moment\nand feel this uneasiness."},{"time":164640,"text":"You could even hear it."},{"time":167360,"text":"Let us cherish the fact"},{"time":169560,"text":"that probably most of you\nhave never been close to a gun."},{"time":175800,"text":"It means the Netherlands\nis a peaceful country."},{"time":180680,"text":"The Netherlands is not at war."},{"time":184120,"text":"It means soldiers are not needed\nto patrol our streets."},{"time":189600,"text":"Guns are not a part of our lives."},{"time":194520,"text":"In many countries,\nit is a different story."},{"time":199440,"text":"In many countries,\npeople are confronted with guns."},{"time":203960,"text":"They are oppressed."},{"time":205840,"text":"They are intimidated --"},{"time":208240,"text":"by warlords,"},{"time":210600,"text":"by terrorists,"},{"time":212760,"text":"by criminals."},{"time":214920,"text":"Weapons can do a lot of harm."},{"time":218040,"text":"They are the cause of much distress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221080,"text":"Why then am I standing before you\nwith this weapon?"},{"time":226080,"text":"Why did I choose the gun as my instrument?"},{"time":231280,"text":"Today I want to tell you why."},{"time":234160,"text":"Today I want to tell you"},{"time":235760,"text":"why I chose the gun\nto create a better world."},{"time":239680,"text":"And I want to tell you\nhow this gun can help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246160,"text":"My story starts in the city of Nijmegen"},{"time":251520,"text":"in the east of the Netherlands,"},{"time":254320,"text":"the city where I was born."},{"time":258480,"text":"My father was a hardworking baker,"},{"time":264800,"text":"but when he had finished\nwork in the bakery,"},{"time":267680,"text":"he often told me and my brother stories."},{"time":271640,"text":"And most of the time,"},{"time":273280,"text":"he told me this story\nI'm going to share with you now."},{"time":278320,"text":"The story of what happened"},{"time":280000,"text":"when he was a conscripted soldier\nin the Dutch armed forces"},{"time":284360,"text":"at the beginning of the Second World War."},{"time":288160,"text":"The Nazis invaded the Netherlands."},{"time":291040,"text":"Their grim plans were evident."},{"time":293840,"text":"They meant to rule by means of repression."},{"time":298360,"text":"Diplomacy had failed to stop the Germans."},{"time":302680,"text":"Only brute force remained."},{"time":306360,"text":"It was our last resort."},{"time":309600,"text":"My father was there to provide it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314040,"text":"As the son of a farmer\nwho knew how to hunt,"},{"time":317880,"text":"my father was an excellent marksman."},{"time":320920,"text":"When he aimed, he never missed."},{"time":324800,"text":"At this decisive moment in Dutch history"},{"time":327840,"text":"my father was positioned\non the bank of the river Waal"},{"time":332680,"text":"near the city of Nijmegen."},{"time":335680,"text":"He had a clear shot at the German soldiers\nwho came to occupy a free country,"},{"time":341920,"text":"his country,"},{"time":343520,"text":"our country."},{"time":345560,"text":"He fired. Nothing happened."},{"time":348720,"text":"He fired again."},{"time":350480,"text":"No German soldier fell to the ground."},{"time":354160,"text":"My father had been given an old gun"},{"time":359000,"text":"that could not even reach\nthe opposite riverbank."},{"time":364200,"text":"Hitler's troops marched on,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and there was nothing\nmy father could do about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371400,"text":"Until the day my father died,"},{"time":374360,"text":"he was frustrated\nabout missing these shots."},{"time":379080,"text":"He could have done something."},{"time":381600,"text":"But with an old gun,"},{"time":383440,"text":"not even the best marksman\nin the armed forces"},{"time":386360,"text":"could have hit the mark."},{"time":389120,"text":"So this story stayed with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393200,"text":"Then in high school,"},{"time":394600,"text":"I was gripped by the stories\nof the Allied soldiers --"},{"time":399440,"text":"soldiers who left the safety\nof their own homes and risked their lives"},{"time":404720,"text":"to liberate a country"},{"time":407840,"text":"and a people that they didn't know."},{"time":411000,"text":"They liberated my birth town."},{"time":414640,"text":"It was then that I decided\nI would take up the gun --"},{"time":420520,"text":"out of respect and gratitude\nfor those men and women"},{"time":425200,"text":"who came to liberate us."},{"time":429000,"text":"From the awareness\nthat sometimes only the gun"},{"time":433840,"text":"can stand between good and evil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438880,"text":"And that is why I took up the gun --"},{"time":442920,"text":"not to shoot,"},{"time":444840,"text":"not to kill,"},{"time":446320,"text":"not to destroy,"},{"time":448600,"text":"but to stop those who would do evil,"},{"time":452360,"text":"to protect the vulnerable,"},{"time":455280,"text":"to defend democratic values,"},{"time":458680,"text":"to stand up for the freedom we have\nto talk here today in Amsterdam"},{"time":465160,"text":"about how we can\nmake the world a better place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469640,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":470880,"text":"I do not stand here today\nto tell you about the glory of weapons."},{"time":477200,"text":"I do not like guns."},{"time":480480,"text":"And once you have been\nunder fire yourself,"},{"time":485080,"text":"it brings home even more clearly"},{"time":487640,"text":"that a gun is not\nsome macho instrument to brag about."},{"time":493600,"text":"I stand here today"},{"time":495120,"text":"to tell you about the use of the gun\nas an instrument of peace and stability."},{"time":503120,"text":"The gun may be one of the most important\ninstruments of peace and stability"},{"time":507480,"text":"that we have in this world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"Now this may sound contradictory to you."},{"time":514400,"text":"But not only have I seen with my own eyes"},{"time":518159,"text":"during my deployments in Lebanon, Sarajevo"},{"time":521206,"text":"and as the Netherlands' Chief of Defence,"},{"time":525040,"text":"this is also supported\nby cold, hard statistics."},{"time":531960,"text":"Violence has declined dramatically\nover the last 500 years."},{"time":538040,"text":"Despite the pictures\nwe are shown daily in the news,"},{"time":542440,"text":"wars between developed countries\nare no longer commonplace."},{"time":547280,"text":"The murder rate in Europe"},{"time":548560,"text":"has dropped by a factor of 30\nsince the Middle Ages."},{"time":553520,"text":"And occurrences\nof civil war and repression"},{"time":556320,"text":"have declined since the end\nof the Cold War."},{"time":560200,"text":"Statistics show that we are living\nin a relatively peaceful era."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566480,"text":"Why?"},{"time":568040,"text":"Why has violence decreased?"},{"time":571280,"text":"Has the human mind changed?"},{"time":573280,"text":"Well, we were talking\nabout the human mind this morning."},{"time":576440,"text":"Did we simply lose\nour beastly impulses for revenge,"},{"time":581280,"text":"for violent rituals,"},{"time":583560,"text":"for pure rage?"},{"time":586360,"text":"Or is there something else?"},{"time":589640,"text":"In his latest book,\nHarvard professor Steven Pinker --"},{"time":593280,"text":"and many other thinkers before him --"},{"time":595680,"text":"concludes that one of the main drivers"},{"time":600520,"text":"behind less violent societies"},{"time":603080,"text":"is the spread of the constitutional state"},{"time":607080,"text":"and the introduction, on a large scale,"},{"time":610288,"text":"of the state monopoly\non the legitimized use of violence --"},{"time":615440,"text":"legitimized by a democratically\nelected government,"},{"time":621120,"text":"legitimized by checks and balances\nand an independent judicial system."},{"time":627640,"text":"In other words, a state monopoly"},{"time":630720,"text":"that has the use of violence\nwell under control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636400,"text":"Such a state monopoly on violence,\nfirst of all, serves as a reassurance."},{"time":644160,"text":"It removes the incentive for an arms race"},{"time":647000,"text":"between potentially hostile groups\nin our societies."},{"time":651520,"text":"Secondly, the presence of penalties"},{"time":654320,"text":"that outweigh the benefits\nof using violence"},{"time":658000,"text":"tips the balance even further."},{"time":661320,"text":"Abstaining from violence"},{"time":663160,"text":"becomes more profitable\nthan starting a war."},{"time":667600,"text":"Now nonviolence starts to work\nlike a flywheel."},{"time":673160,"text":"It enhances peace even further."},{"time":676840,"text":"Where there is no conflict,\ntrade flourishes."},{"time":681480,"text":"And trade is another important\nincentive against violence."},{"time":686520,"text":"With trade, there's mutual interdependency\nand mutual gain between parties."},{"time":693400,"text":"And when there is mutual gain,\nboth sides stand to lose more"},{"time":698480,"text":"than they would gain\nif they started a war."},{"time":702880,"text":"War is simply no longer the best option,"},{"time":707360,"text":"and that is why violence has decreased."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713080,"text":"This, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":714880,"text":"is the rationale behind the existence\nof my armed forces."},{"time":720560,"text":"The armed forces implement\nthe state monopoly on violence."},{"time":725640,"text":"We do this in a legitimized way"},{"time":728120,"text":"only after our democracy\nhas asked us to do so."},{"time":735080,"text":"It is this legitimate,\ncontrolled use of the gun"},{"time":740280,"text":"that has contributed greatly"},{"time":742120,"text":"to reducing the statistics of war,\nconflict and violence around the globe."},{"time":748520,"text":"It is this participation\nin peacekeeping missions"},{"time":752080,"text":"that has led to the resolution\nof many civil wars."},{"time":756760,"text":"My soldiers use the gun\nas an instrument of peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763280,"text":"And this is exactly\nwhy failed states are so dangerous."},{"time":768640,"text":"Failed states have no legitimized,\ndemocratically controlled use of force."},{"time":774240,"text":"Failed states do not know of the gun\nas an instrument of peace and stability."},{"time":781600,"text":"That is why failed states can drag down\na whole region into chaos and conflict."},{"time":788960,"text":"That is why spreading the concept\nof the constitutional state"},{"time":792880,"text":"is such an important aspect\nof our foreign missions."},{"time":797520,"text":"That is why we are trying\nto build a judicial system"},{"time":801280,"text":"right now in Afghanistan."},{"time":804560,"text":"That is why we train\npolice officers, we train judges,"},{"time":808840,"text":"we train public prosecutors\naround the world."},{"time":812600,"text":"And that is why --"},{"time":813960,"text":"and in the Netherlands,\nwe are very unique in that --"},{"time":817280,"text":"that is why the Dutch constitution states"},{"time":821040,"text":"that one of the main tasks\nof the armed forces"},{"time":824320,"text":"is to uphold and promote\nthe international rule of law."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831120,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":832720,"text":"looking at this gun, we are confronted\nwith the ugly side of the human mind."},{"time":840640,"text":"Every day I hope that politicians,\ndiplomats, development workers"},{"time":846680,"text":"can turn conflict into peace"},{"time":850160,"text":"and threat"},{"time":852200,"text":"into hope."},{"time":854040,"text":"And I hope that one day\narmies can be disbanded"},{"time":858840,"text":"and humans will find a way\nof living together"},{"time":861760,"text":"without violence and oppression."},{"time":865200,"text":"But until that day comes,"},{"time":868880,"text":"we will have to make ideals\nand human failure"},{"time":874280,"text":"meet somewhere in the middle."},{"time":876920,"text":"Until that day comes,\nI stand for my father"},{"time":881960,"text":"who tried to shoot the Nazis\nwith an old gun."},{"time":886200,"text":"I stand for my men and women\nwho are prepared to risk their lives"},{"time":892280,"text":"for a less violent world for all of us."},{"time":897000,"text":"I stand for this soldier\nwho suffered partial hearing loss"},{"time":902920,"text":"and sustained permanent\ninjuries to her leg,"},{"time":906080,"text":"when she was hit by a rocket\non a mission in Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":912600,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":914400,"text":"until the day comes\nwhen we can do away with the gun,"},{"time":919680,"text":"I hope we all agree"},{"time":922560,"text":"that peace and stability\ndo not come free of charge."},{"time":927840,"text":"It takes hard work,\noften behind the scenes."},{"time":933640,"text":"It takes good equipment\nand well-trained, dedicated soldiers."},{"time":939280,"text":"I hope you will support\nthe efforts of our armed forces"},{"time":944240,"text":"to train soldiers like this young captain"},{"time":947280,"text":"and provide her with a good gun,"},{"time":950200,"text":"instead of the bad gun\nmy father was given."},{"time":953800,"text":"I hope you will support our soldiers\nwhen they are out there,"},{"time":959520,"text":"when they come home"},{"time":962000,"text":"and when they are injured\nand need our care."},{"time":965840,"text":"They put their lives on the line,\nfor us, for you,"},{"time":970680,"text":"and we cannot let them down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974640,"text":"I hope you will respect my soldiers,"},{"time":979000,"text":"this soldier with this gun."},{"time":981920,"text":"Because she wants a better world."},{"time":985240,"text":"Because she makes an active\ncontribution to a better world,"},{"time":990080,"text":"just like all of us here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":993880,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":995360,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}